---
title: Quick Sticky Asian Chicken & Celery Slaw with Roast Pumpkin & Potato Chunks
description: This chicken has layers upon layers of flavour, first being cooked in our staple sweet soy seasoning, then being tossed in sweet chilli and soy! A crunchy, creamy slaw and chunks of roast veggies act as the perfect side-kicks to this superstar dish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
